byline.original: By STEVEN ERLANGER and ALISON SMALE

lead_paragraph: Vice President Mike Pence offered reassurances Saturday to anxious European leaders, but he also warned that they must spend more on defense.

headline.main: In Munich, Pence Says U.S. Commitment to NATO Is ‘Unwavering’
